data.value: The SSS(Student Servise Software) is the software designed to provide Universities, colleges or School to manage all the basic information for students in onle place, information like teacher details, subject details, etc. This software's primary gole is to provide the all basic information at one place withiout disturbing other's and to remove the old system or technology of maintianing these data or recods, which is pen and pappers and revolutinize the process by overcomming all the limitation of the existing system.
